ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands

Class DeployLaserBeaconCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands.ShipCommand
      • ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands.DeployLaserBeaconCommand

  • public class DeployLaserBeaconCommand
extends ShipCommand
    A command to deploy a laser beacon from a ship.

    Pairs of laser beacons draw a line in space. The first beacon deployed represents the starting point of the line; the next beacon will terminate the line. Lines do not follow the ship's path-- they simply connect two beacons directly.
